 about this now called project Orion written by the son of freemon dyson whose father worked on the  origonal orion project.<br>
Also you should go to library, and the internet,and study<br>
up on high explosive shaped charges, and high explosive<br>
lenses which are used to make the total force of<br>
a high explosives shock waves go in one direction,<br>
or to one place by focusing  their shock waves  on them .<br>
 This real, and important  technology is used to achieve<br>
an  implosion wave In A-bombs  by focusing 100 % of the force of the shock waves from the detonation of the  high explosives on the atomic pit when they explode.<br>
It is used for the demolition of bridges and buildings.<br>
It is also used to make military ordnance for destroying<br>
tanks et el .<br>
You can also find some information about this at the high energy weapons archive of the nuclear physcists Gary Sublette on the internet.<br>
You may also want to arrange to get a summary of the <br>
records of the origional manhattan project for your self<br>
 as well.<br>
Then you should read, and study all these things carefully.<br>
<br>
I have studied  all of these things and many more things <br>
like this for 30 years.<br>
Research high explosive shaped charges,  and high explosive  lenses in the library too along with  basic nuclear physics et el , basic nuclear weapon design , chemical , and nuclear rocketry,<br>
nuclear reactors, electric ion and plasma rocket engines <br>
  et el as I have already  done for 30 years to learn about all of these things in detail.  Also go learn abut some of these things at the various nasa sites on the web such as that of Jpl, and the electric rocket  proplusion web site  of the of  The aerospace engineer Woodmansee who works at at JPl , and so on.<br>
Tim<br>
